lyrics:
[Verse]
I must scream but I got no air
Lost in silence, drowning in despair
In this world, my voice remains unheard
Beneath the surface, my soul is blurred

[Chorus]
Feels like running under water
Struggling, can't break free, going farther
Oh, can't you see my desperate plea
I'm suffocating, won't you set me free
style: pop, black male vocalist with strong voice, song-message to the world, 72 BPM
